    • eCW will send clinical documents when requested by external connected sites and will also request clinical documents from external connected sites and display them in eCW.
  • Opted In: Send Documents Only
    • eCW will send clinical documents when requested by external connected sites. eCW will not request any clinical documents from external connected sites.

    • eCW will request clinical documents from external connected sites and display them in eCW. eCW will not send any clinical documents to external connected sites.

    • eCW will neither send clinical documents to nor request clinical documents from external connected sites.
